   13 (12) print 6 в†’ P[3,5]                          (8) print 5 в†’ Cв‚‚[]            6 5
   15 (14) в†ђ west             (2) print 1 в†’ Cв‚Ѓ[1]   (6) tв‚Ѓ SPLIT вЂ” Cв‚ѓ at (7) east  1
   16 P at (12) west          Cв‚Ѓ at (4) east        Cв‚‚ at (4) west    Cв‚ѓ at (8) east
